Compiling glib2.0 programs on RISC OS

C flags
-I/LibGLib2:glib-2.0

Linking flags for shared libraries
-LLibGLib2: -lglib-2.0

Linking flags for static libraries
-LLibGLib2: -lglib-2.0 -LLibGetText: -lintl

For running of shared programs you will need the
libglib2.0 runtime and the libgettext runtime.

